Package pluto.views

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AbstractView
    Abstract class of views in the MVC design pattern.
    CourseBuildView
    "build" view for course resource
    CourseEditView
    "edit" view for course resource inherits the build view, but loads in the data
    CourseIndexInstructorView
    View for courses instructed by Instructor
    CourseIndexStudentView
    View for all the student's taken courses
    CourseOfSubjectInstructorView
    View for showing the courses of one subject.
    CourseOfSubjectStudentView
    View for showing the courses of one subject.
    CourseShowView
    "show" view for course resource Actually shows the students that took this course
    DashboardView
    Welcome view for the user.
    LoginView
    "login" view for user resource
    RegistrationView
    "build" view for user resource Registration view is connected to login page
    SubjectBuildView
    "build" view for subject resource
    SubjectEditView
    "edit" view for subject resource
    SubjectIndexInstructorView
    View for the subjects coordinated by the instructor.
    SubjectIndexStudentView
    View for the subjects of taken courses by the student.
    SubjectIndexView
    View for taking courses, shows the available subjects, can go on to take courses after selecting one subject.
    UserEditView
    "edit" view for user resource won't show password field for the administrator (they can edit any user)
    UserIndexView
    "index" view for user resource only admins see this
